sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser (elemen video)
    participant F as Frontend :8081
    participant A as Backend API :8082
    participant S as Penyimpanan data/media

    B->>F: GET /media/stream/id/5<br/>Range: bytes=0-
    F->>A: GET /media/stream/id/5?user_id=1<br/>Authorization + X-Timestamp + X-Signature + Range
    A->>A: Verifikasi Basic Auth, timestamp, HMAC
    A->>A: Cek kepemilikan file di MySQL (by id)
    A->>S: fopen + fseek sesuai Range
    A-->>F: 206 Partial Content<br/>Content-Range: bytes 0-.../ukuran
    F-->>B: 206 diteruskan (relay per 8KB)
    Note over B,F: Pengguna menggeser (seek) posisi video
    B->>F: GET /media/stream/id/5<br/>Range: bytes=1048576-
    F->>A: Range diteruskan + signature baru
    A-->>F: 206 Content-Range: bytes 1048576-.../ukuran
    F-->>B: Video melompat tanpa mengunduh ulang seluruh file
